                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row rowsep="1" class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">(Signature and Title of Contractor </p>
                        <p class="- topic/p ">Representative) _______________</p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row rowsep="1" class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">By</p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row rowsep="0" class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">Date</p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
               </tbody>
            </tgroup>
         </table>
         <p class="- topic/p "/>
         <p class="- topic/p ">*If only a release is procured, delete this article; if an assignment is procured, use the clause at 
               <xref outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                  class="- topic/xref "
                  base="i1382626"
                  href="252.227-7011.dita#DFARS_252.227-7011">252.227-7011</xref>
            .</p>
         <p class="- topic/p ">**When the Contractor is an individual, change “successors” to “heirs”; if a partnership, modify appropriately.</p>
         <p outputclass="Endofclause" class="- topic/p ">(End of clause) </p>
